<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h3 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Zipper 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        functionality and branding
      </span>
    </h3>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      The zipper on a Balenciaga handbag is an important feature to examine when authenticating the bag. Here are some things to look for:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Lampo branding:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The zipper should be marked “Lampo,” a trusted brand used by Balenciaga for its high-quality zippers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Be wary of low prices:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          If the price seems too good to be true, it probably is. Authentic Balenciaga bags are high-end luxury items and are rarely sold at significantly discounted prices.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Functional and easy to use:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The zipper should be functional and easy to use, gliding smoothly without any resistance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Secure attachment:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The zipper should be securely attached to the bag, with no loose threads or signs of poor craftsmanship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Smooth, even motion:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The zipper should have a smooth, even motion, reflecting the high standards of Balenciaga’s manufacturing process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="body-text tac block-bottom-text w-100">
      By paying attention to these details, you can verify the authenticity of the zipper and, by extension, the entire bag.
  </p>
</div>

